Rules.InvariantScript:
"data:image/svg+xml;utf8," & EncodeUrl(
    Substitute(
        Substitute(
    comp_card2_v01.Icon_URL
    ,
    "currentColor" ,
     If(
        comp_card2_v01.IsTrue_DarkMode , 
        "#ffffff" , 
        "#222222"
     )
    )
    , 
    "width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24" ,
    "width='16' height='16' viewBox='-12 -12 48 48"
    )
)
